讀得開心 d 同埋之後萬一做唔到 pilot 都可以係自己有興趣既 field 做<br />\n<br />\n3. Cadet requirement 唔需要 cpl, 有 cpl 可以入 advance entry<br />\n<br />\n4. 你講直接做 pilot 果 d 係要有一定飛行時數 (起碼都講 ~700hr total time 先有機有得 in)<br />\n<br />\n5. Cadet 係最直接渠道<br />\n<br />\n6. 比心機用呢幾年去 join 唔同 program 去加深對飛行既理解 (至於有咩 program 靠自己研究啦)<br />\n<br />\n7. 想試下飛既感覺可以去外國飛下<br />\n<br />\n8. 加油"},{"pid":"a90a611ec57f3bc943e0cf48f7a6f7dba7ff9174","tid":1495952,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T12:35:47.000Z","msg":"DACP<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa172a7489a94830b8542ae023e0942a0224011","tid":1495952,"uid":311597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T12:59:17.000Z","msg":"有cpl仲考cadet<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a526b4823f1fd3e2555729e3c100179a966b86aa","tid":1495952,"uid":336761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09919f48d42a8184f3b8091fc96ee6086ab375d8","tid":1495952,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:31:59.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到, 少少意見<br />\n<br />\n1. 大學讀咩科同做 pilot 冇咩關係<br />\n<br />\n2. 對航空有興趣既, 當然讀 aviation related 會讀得開心 d 同埋之後萬一做唔到 pilot 都可以係自己有興趣既 field 做<br />\n<br />\n3. Cadet requirement 唔需要 cpl, 有 cpl 可以入 advance entry<br />\n<br />\n4. 你講直接做 pilot 果 d 係要有一定飛行時數 (起碼都講 ~700hr total time 先有機有得 in)<br />\n<br />\n5. Cadet 係最直接渠道<br />\n<br />\n6. 比心機用呢幾年去 join 唔同 program 去加深對飛行既理解 (至於有咩 program 靠自己研究啦)<br />\n<br />\n7. 想試下飛既感覺可以去外國飛下<br />\n<br />\n8. 加油"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:53:33.000Z","msg":"第一點<br />\n其實cadet多唔多讀engine或者aviation呢類相關學科<br />\n如果講到係讀account finance呢啲會唔會差距大得濟<br />\n<img